Comprehensive digital  twin approach 

• Realistic simulation and validation of products, machines, lines and complete plants

• Seamless flow of information from the real and digital world

• Holistic view on 30+ sustainability impacts along the value chain (CO₂, fresh water consumption, human toxicity etc.)

• Continuous optimization loop to achieve greater sustainability (design, production and performance)